data.description: **Price Improvement!**You won't be disappointed w/ this 3 bedroom, 2.1 bathroom including an  inviting living room w/gas fireplace, formal dining room, and spacious kitchen with appliances. 9 ft ceilings throughout.  1st. floor laundry.  Full basement with 10ft ceilings.  Side drive with 2 car garage and private covered entertainment area in the rear of the home. Inviting Park like  area near the home. 2 minutes to Metra train station. Property is being sold as is and room sizes are estimated. This one needs your finishing touches to make this one yours!
